\fs24
\b Receipt Scanner iOS Conversion Steps\b0\par
\par
Project ZIP: ReceiptScanner_iOS_Handover.zip\par
Target output: Apple iOS app (.ipa)\par
\par
\b 1) Prepare Mac Environment\b0\par
- Install latest stable Flutter\par
- Install Xcode and open once to finish setup\par
- Install CocoaPods (pod)\par
- Sign in with Apple Developer account in Xcode\par
\par
\b 2) Open Project\b0\par
Unzip ReceiptScanner_iOS_Handover.zip and open Terminal in the project root folder.\par
\par
\b 3) Build Commands\b0\par
\f1 flutter clean\f0\par
\f1 flutter pub get\f0\par
\f1 cd ios\f0\par
\f1 pod install\f0\par
\f1 cd ..\f0\par
\f1 flutter build ipa --release\f0\par
\par
\b 4) If Signing Error Appears\b0\par
- Open ios/Runner.xcworkspace in Xcode\par
- Go to Runner > Signing & Capabilities\par
- Set Team, Bundle Identifier, and Signing Certificate\par
- Then build archive from Xcode: Product > Archive\par
\par
\b 5) Output Location\b0\par
build/ios/ipa/\par
\par
\b 6) Client Delivery Options\b0\par
- Upload via App Store Connect / TestFlight\par
- Or export IPA from Xcode Organizer for internal distribution\par
\par
\b 7) Quick Verification Before Upload\b0\par
- Open app and check scan workflow\par
- Save and edit invoice\par
- Invoice list and reports\par
- Export/share actions\par
}
